{"type": "article", "id": 2609, "title": "PLUMBER 小时钟", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-28T08:40:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232307uKprIhJaSwyH7xsj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计品牌 Bozu 近日推出一款用来放置在桌面上的小型时钟 PLUMBER ，出自香港设计工作室 Rooflab 的设计师 Andrea Bellotto 之手。PLUMBER 的整体造型采用简单的几何形状，像是水管连接处，高光陶瓷是其主要材质。不同于其他时钟专注于表面的设计，Andrea Bellotto 更注重于这款时钟背面的弧线设计，不经意间透出呆萌的感觉。目前，PLUMBER 在上海康定路 361 号的共禾京品有售。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232305YyFxQG9dfgKU3uMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232305PXhf3T7RqGLWdBZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232305fPc94vhJo2Y7rIMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323062VsuAlZoKBgYem18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}